  "title": "St. Leonards Bay",
  "summary": "随便跑了一个海滩去拍照，运气很好，这里很美。 台风过境，一棵大树被连根拔起。顺着悬崖被抛到海滩上。 台风对周围 […]",
  "content": "<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/9ecc5ccf-4218-4aee-b5ce-347e97ce9ecc.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>随便跑了一个海滩去拍照，运气很好，这里很美。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/9ecc5ccb-9ad7-49d7-8793-6a44f01929ae.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>台风过境，一棵大树被连根拔起。顺着悬崖被抛到海滩上。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/9ecc5cc7-3461-4cf1-a6b3-34a476ad83ad.jpg?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>台风对周围的楼梯造成了破坏。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/9ecc5c53-08ab-4eff-aaa2-ce2f18191987.webp?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>周围随便逛一逛。天气不太好。随时要下雨。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"575\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/9ecc5c53-0395-4973-93aa-4b4a1b7d1ead.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>然后竟然有人在划船。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/9ecc5c74-91a6-4466-bf8f-21cb55b6fbe7.jpg?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>远处的山是Rangitoto，我很多年前去过一次。很想再去一次。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"575\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/9ecc5c53-57f8-4e53-b2a9-54bd07f44a14.webp?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>说时迟那是快，瞬间就变天了。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"575\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/9ecc5c52-feff-4bb4-adc7-cc6b9a14f053.webp?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>",
  "image": "https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/9ecc5ccf-4218-4aee-b5ce-347e97ce9ecc.jpg",
  "publishedAt": "2025-05-02T19:45:52Z",
